<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1031305.htm">微信推送 iOS 7.0.16 测试版，新增「不显示」功能</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1367294" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/banner.jpg" alt="" width="1266" height="474" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/banner.jpg 1266w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/banner-360x135.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/banner-768x288.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/banner-1024x383.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1266px) 100vw, 1266px" /></p>
<p>威锋网消息，微信推送了 iOS 7.0.16 测试版，新增了「不显示」对话功能。在该版本中，用户如果左滑联系人对话，除了会出现原有的「已读」和「删除」外，还有一个「不显示」按钮。</p>
<p>选择「不显示」后，该对话将会从列表消失，但保留聊天记录，并将于该对话有新的消息时再出现。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/science/1031421.htm">泰坦尼克号的沉没，可能是受到太阳耀斑活动影响</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1367295" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/header-titanic-solar-storms.jpg" alt="" width="2500" height="1201" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/header-titanic-solar-storms.jpg 2500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/header-titanic-solar-storms-360x173.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/header-titanic-solar-storms-768x369.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/header-titanic-solar-storms-1024x492.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px" /></p>
<p>一篇新论文推测，太阳耀斑活动可能是导致泰坦尼克号沉没且难以施救的原因。</p>
<p>泰坦尼克号于 1912 年 4 月 14 日沉没，新的研究发现，就在该船沉没的当晚，北半球正遭受一场中度至严重的磁暴袭击。论文推测，磁暴可能改变了泰坦尼克号的导航读数，影响了它的计划航线和船员在发送 SOS 信号后分享的位置信息。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.bococn.com/eo/product/">Earsopen 发布真无线骨传导蓝牙耳机 Earsopen TW-1</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1367296" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/0985_meitu_1.jpg" alt="" width="903" height="308" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/0985_meitu_1.jpg 903w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/0985_meitu_1-360x123.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/0985_meitu_1-768x262.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 903px) 100vw, 903px" /></p>
<p>日本品牌 Earsopen 逸鸥发布真无线骨传导蓝牙耳机 Earsopen TW-1，定价 1688 元。耳机采用 T 型结构，类似「扣」在耳朵上，每侧重量耳机重量为 9g；IPX7 防水，下雨天和运动场景均适用。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1367297" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3-10.jpg" alt="" width="624" height="457" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3-10.jpg 624w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/3-10-360x264.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 624px) 100vw, 624px" /></p>
<p>Earsopen TW-1 由骨骼经过耳蜗直接被听觉神经所感知，因此在听歌的时候也能保持对外界声音的警觉，同时也可降低鼓膜的负担和听力损失的风险。</p>
